<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>MacMenuBar.com (中文)</title><link>https://macmenubar.com</link><description>精心整理的1300多款Mac菜单栏应用目录</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 09 Apr 2026 11:58:26 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>丝波语音</title><link>https://macmenubar.com/silkwave-voice/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Silkwave_Voice.webp"&gt;&lt;img alt="Silkwave Voice" height="580" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://macmenubar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Silkwave_Voice.webp" width="800"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Silkwave Voice 可同时录制麦克风和系统音频，并使用苹果的设备端模型实时转录所有内容。无需网络连接，无需API费用，无需订阅。通过苹果智能生成摘要。完全私密。&lt;/p&gt;
